            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "During the tough time of  pandemic, when students and parents were anxious about stagnation of the education, SLPS  took away all our worries by conducting online classes which were  not taken for just name sake rather provided best experiential innovative learning with diversified  knowledge from different fields. I acknowledge the creative thinking of school management in framing the child-friendly curriculum  and also appreciate the assiduous efforts of all the Kavi Nagar branch teachers who with their grit and industriousness have made the progressive learning possible.  I definitely recommend this school to all those parents who look forward towards a holistic developed personality of their wards.",
